===[[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]===
{{main|Lt. Surge (Genetic Apex 226)}}
Lt. Surge makes an appearance as a {{TCG|Supporter}} card in [[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]'s first expansion, {{TCGP|Genetic Apex}}. When the player plays this card, they may move all {{TCG|Lightning}} {{TCG|Energy}} attached to their Benched Pokémon and to a {{TCGP|Raichu}}, {{TCGP|Electrode}}, or {{TCGP|Electabuzz}} in their Active Spot.

